          </h3>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-xs">
            
            <!-- 單字項目 -->
            <div class="word-badge-btn flex items-center justify-between p-2.5 rounded-xl bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 text-left">
              <div class="overflow-hidden">
                <span class="font-bold text-indigo-300 block text-[10px] uppercase">1. ch- endings</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-black tracking-wide">lunch</span>
              </div>
              <span class="star-badge text-gray-500 text-sm">☆</span>
            </div>

            <div class="word-badge-btn flex items-center justify-between p-2.5 rounded-xl bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 text-left">
              <div class="overflow-hidden">
                <span class="font-bold text-indigo-300 block text-[10px] uppercase">2. wh- sound</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-black tracking-wide">when</span>
              </div>
              <span class="star-badge text-gray-500 text-sm">☆</span>
            </div>

            <div class="word-badge-btn flex items-center justify-between p-2.5 rounded-xl bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 text-left">
              <div class="overflow-hidden">
                <span class="font-bold text-indigo-300 block text-[10px] uppercase">3. th- sound</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-black tracking-wide">this</span>
              </div>
              <span class="star-badge text-gray-500 text-sm">☆</span>
            </div>

            <div class="word-badge-btn flex items-center justify-between p-2.5 rounded-xl bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 text-left">
              <div class="overflow-hidden">
                <span class="font-bold text-indigo-300 block text-[10px] uppercase">4. sh- sound</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-black tracking-wide">shop</span>
              </div>
              <span class="star-badge text-gray-500 text-sm">☆</span>
            </div>

            <div class="word-badge-btn flex items-center justify-between p-2.5 rounded-xl bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 text-left">
              <div class="overflow-hidden">
                <span class="font-bold text-indigo-300 block text-[10px] uppercase">5. -ph endings</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-black tracking-wide">graph</span>
              </div>
              <span class="star-badge text-gray-500 text-sm">☆</span>
            </div>

            <div class="word-badge-btn flex items-center justify-between p-2.5 rounded-xl bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 text-left">
              <div class="overflow-hidden">
                <span class="font-bold text-indigo-300 block text-[10px] uppercase">6. wh- sound</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-black tracking-wide">white</span>
              </div>
              <span class="star-badge text-gray-500 text-sm">☆</span>
            </div>

            <div class="word-badge-btn flex items-center justify-between p-2.5 rounded-xl bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 text-left">
              <div class="overflow-hidden">
                <span class="font-bold text-indigo-300 block text-[10px] uppercase">7. -th endings</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-black tracking-wide">teeth</span>
              </div>
              <span class="star-badge text-gray-500 text-sm">☆</span>
            </div>

            <div class="word-badge-btn flex items-center justify-between p-2.5 rounded-xl bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 text-left">
              <div class="overflow-hidden">
                <span class="font-bold text-indigo-300 block text-[10px] uppercase">8. ph- sound</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-black tracking-wide">phone</span>
              </div>
              <span class="star-badge text-gray-500 text-sm">☆</span>
            </div>

            <div class="word-badge-btn flex items-center justify-between p-2.5 rounded-xl bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 text-left">
              <div class="overflow-hidden">
                <span class="font-bold text-indigo-300 block text-[10px] uppercase">9. ch- double</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-black tracking-wide">church</span>
              </div>
              <span class="star-badge text-gray-500 text-sm">☆</span>
            </div>

            <div class="word-badge-btn flex items-center justify-between p-2.5 rounded-xl bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 text-left">
              <div class="overflow-hidden">
                <span class="font-bold text-indigo-300 block text-[10px] uppercase">10. ch- sound</span>
